#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.tanh.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.tanh"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:1 of
msgid "Compute hyperbolic tangent element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算双曲正切值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:3 of
msgid "Equivalent to ``mt.sinh(x)/np.cosh(x)`` or ``-1j * mt.tan(1j*x)``."
msgstr "等价于 ``mt.sinh(x)/np.cosh(x)`` 或 ``-1j * mt.tan(1j*x)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:5 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有与输入广播兼容的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:17 of
msgid "**y** -- The corresponding hyperbolic tangent values."
msgstr "**y** -- 对应的双曲正切值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:22 of
msgid ""
"If `out` is provided, the function writes the result into it, and returns"
" a reference to `out`.  (See Examples)"
msgstr ""
"如果提供了 `out`，函数会将结果写入其中，并返回对 `out` 的引用。（参见示例"
"）"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:26 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:27 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I. A. Stegun, Handbook of Mathematical Functions. New "
"York, NY: Dover, 1972, pg. 83. http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"
msgstr ""
"M. Abramowitz 和 I. A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》。纽约：Dover，1972年，第"
"83页。http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.tanh.tanh:31 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Hyperbolic function\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperbolic_function"
msgstr "维基百科，“双曲函数”，http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperbolic_function"

